ADAPTIVE CHECKERS VERSION 3

This package is deployment-ready for Render.

Included:
- render.yaml for Render Blueprint deployment
- Node/WebSocket server
- public game files

What this solves:
- public web deployment config is included
- WebSocket-compatible hosting config is included
- free-tier-compatible setup is included

What still must happen outside this package:
- the package must be uploaded to your own GitHub account
- Render must deploy it from that repo
- after deployment, Render gives the public URL

Once deployed:
- you open the public URL
- click Δημιουργία Δωματίου
- send the 4-digit code to your friend
- your friend opens the same public URL and joins with the code

